modules.description: This module enables type-safe manipulation of Frei0r plugins through operations that load plugins, inspect metadata (e.g., parameter types, color models), and process multimedia data using typed big arrays. It centers on functional access and transformation of plugin parameters—such as colors, floats, and boolean flags—while supporting use cases like real-time video filtering, color correction, and generative visual effects via its `update` family of data-processing functions.
